token_info.name: Tensegrity Between The Discrete And The Continuous (Bull)
token_info.description: This series takes images captured by Edweard Muybridge in the late 1800's and converts them into solid structures. By interpolating the movement originally captured as discrete elements, I am able to explroe the tension between the discrete and the continuous. More can be read about this project here: https://tywenkelly.medium.com/tweening-67eac3560121
